FEATURES INCLUDED (ENTERPRISE TIER)

Includes all Pro features PLUS:
- mTLS client certificate authentication
- Multi-server routing (route to multiple upstream MCP servers)
- SIEM audit log shipping (Splunk, Datadog, etc.)
- OpenTelemetry distributed tracing (Jaeger, Tempo)
- Per-tool rate limiting
- Admin guard tools (key management, audit viewer, config generator)
- Priority support

SUPPORT & SLA

Enterprise tier includes:
- Priority email support (4hr response time for critical issues)
- Dedicated Slack channel (for 10+ seats)
- Security updates with 24hr SLA
- Bug fixes with priority escalation
- Quarterly check-ins
- Custom feature requests (subject to approval)
- Access to all documentation and training materials

Contact: austin@botzr.dev
Enterprise portal: https://mcp-guard.io/enterprise

SEAT LICENSING

Each license is valid for a specified number of "seats" (individual users).
A seat is defined as:
- One human user who operates mcp-guard
- One machine/instance running mcp-guard in production

Seat usage is tracked via license validation. Exceeding seat limits will
result in license validation failures.

